{"tid":1884230,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"WHO，醫返都殘肺 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-02-17T12:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T14:56:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6d2283571a1863526616090a264243464476d001","tid":1884230,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T12:57:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200217/20863584/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200217%2F20863584%2F&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=1e9d88f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200217%2F20863584%2F&h=141d1798\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200217/20863584/</a><br />\n<br />\nWHO，醫返都殘肺 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200217/large/1581836638_b9a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200217%2Flarge%2F1581836638_b9a1.jpg&h=3680b00b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一，武肺進入高峰抑或未算最高峰？還有更高的嗎？（有嘅，請市民耐心等候「拐點」或者習總的生物安全法落實。）<br />\n<br />\n二，林奠用250億公帑幫自己那句「再提封關已經冇乜意思」埋單，林奠帶領政府高官打邊爐抗疫，港人中晒招，點解佢還未封鋪執笠？還可以用250億救佢自己個市？（因為佢嗰個，係獨市！）<br />\n<br />\n三，口罩要自製自救，250億「正苦水」唔會發落去泛民素人區議會，只會一如既往，自動流入建制口袋，講粗口最大聲的麥氏工會，撈到幾多億？審計署夠膽篤佢嗎？（處長即刻扮衛生署，十問柒唔知。藍屍死性不改，就算武肺冚家拎，都唔撐獨立調查。）<br />\n<br />\n四，護士宿舍污穢過公廁，世界級，鄭司長花二百萬裝修完官邸但唔住，秘密搬去老公的半山豪宅，條數點計？（終於攞到分！林奠將官邸徵用做隔離，安置武漢和鑽石號回港者。）<br />\n<br />\n五，世衛「譚得失」唔敢得失強國，但下屬推測武肺隨時令全球三分二人口感染，講出人話，明插中國。雞珍要再哽咽多少次護主？（WHO被網民譏為Wuhan分會，與打邊爐同一家族，已確診感染，病情危重，醫返都殘肺。） <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"d5c23c97c62c9bdbf8aa5a998cb01767ab952286","tid":1884230,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:56:08.000Z","msg":"議員日日鬧爆支共無人理<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=621741a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"}]}